#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:2
msgid "lmcache query"
msgstr "lmcache 查询"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache query`` command sends a single OpenAI-compatible inference "
"request and reports token and latency metrics. It has two targets:"
msgstr "``lmcache query`` 命令发送一个单一的兼容 OpenAI 的推理请求，并报告令牌和延迟指标。它有两个目标："

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:11
msgid "``engine`` — send one request to a serving engine's HTTP API."
msgstr "``engine`` — 向服务引擎的 HTTP API 发送一个请求。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:12
msgid "``kvcache`` — query KV-cache endpoints (not implemented yet)."
msgstr "``kvcache`` — 查询 KV Cache 端点（尚未实现）。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:16
msgid "query engine"
msgstr "查询引擎"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:18
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The ``query engine`` subcommand sends one request to the engine API and "
"reports metrics. ``--prompt`` supports placeholders: ``{lmcache}`` loads "
"``lmcache/cli/documents/lmcache.txt``, and custom documents can be passed"
" with ``--documents NAME=PATH``. The prompt token count is taken directly"
" from the usage data reported by the engine (``stream_options: "
"{include_usage: true}``)."
msgstr "``query engine`` 子命令向引擎 API 发送一个请求并报告指标。 ``--prompt`` 支持占位符： ``{lmcache}`` 加载 ``lmcache/cli/documents/lmcache.txt``，并且可以通过 ``--documents NAME=PATH`` 传递自定义文档。提示的令牌计数直接来自引擎报告的使用数据 (``stream_options: {include_usage: true}``)。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:45
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:51
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:52
msgid "Required"
msgstr "必需"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:53
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:54
msgid "``--url URL``"
msgstr "``--url URL``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:55 ../../source/cli/query.rst:58
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:56
msgid "Serving engine base URL (e.g. ``http://localhost:8000/v1``)."
msgstr "服务引擎基础 URL（例如 ``http://localhost:8000/v1``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:57
msgid "``--prompt TEXT``"
msgstr "``--prompt TEXT``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:59
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Prompt text with optional ``{name}`` placeholders. ``{lmcache}`` expands "
"to the bundled sample document."
msgstr "带有可选 ``{name}`` 占位符的提示文本。 ``{lmcache}`` 展开为捆绑的示例文档。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:61
msgid "``--model ID``"
msgstr "``--model ID``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:62 ../../source/cli/query.rst:66
#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:69 ../../source/cli/query.rst:72
#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:76 ../../source/cli/query.rst:79
#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:83 ../../source/cli/query.rst:86
#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:89
msgid "No"
msgstr "不"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:63
msgid ""
"Model ID for the serving engine. Auto-detected from the engine's reported"
" usage if omitted."
msgstr "服务引擎的模型 ID。如果省略，将根据引擎报告的使用情况自动检测。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:65
msgid "``--max-tokens N``"
msgstr "``--max-tokens N``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:67
msgid "Maximum completion tokens (default: 128)."
msgstr "最大完成令牌数（默认：128）。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:68
msgid "``--timeout SECS``"
msgstr "``--timeout SECS``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:70
msgid "HTTP timeout in seconds (default: 30)."
msgstr "HTTP 超时（单位：秒，默认值：30）。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:71
msgid "``--documents NAME=PATH``"
msgstr "``--documents NAME=PATH``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:73
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Load file text for ``{NAME}`` in ``--prompt``. Accepts one or more "
"``NAME=PATH`` values."
msgstr "在 ``--prompt`` 中加载 ``{NAME}`` 的文件文本。接受一个或多个 ``NAME=PATH`` 值。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:75
msgid "``--completions``"
msgstr "``--completions``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:77
msgid "Use ``POST /v1/completions`` only."
msgstr "仅使用 ``POST /v1/completions``。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:78
msgid "``--chat-first``"
msgstr "``--chat-first``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:80
msgid "Try ``/v1/chat/completions`` first, then fall back to ``/v1/completions``."
msgstr "首先尝试 ``/v1/chat/completions``，然后回退到 ``/v1/completions``。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:82
msgid "``--format``"
msgstr "``--format``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:84
msgid "Output format: ``terminal`` (default) or ``json``."
msgstr "输出格式：``terminal``（默认）或``json``。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:85
msgid "``--output PATH``"
msgstr "``--output PATH``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:87
msgid "Save metrics to a file (format follows ``--format``)."
msgstr "将指标保存到文件中（格式遵循 ``--format``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:88
msgid "``-q`` / ``--quiet``"
msgstr "``-q`` / ``--quiet``"

#: ../../source/cli/query.rst:90
msgid "Suppress stdout output. Exit code only."
msgstr "抑制标准输出。仅返回退出代码。"

